Package org.enhydra.shark.instancepersistence.dodsselective

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DODSSelectivePersistenceManager
    This DODS 'selective' implementation of InstancePersistence API checks for the extended attribute called 'Transient', and if it exists, it doesn't persist given process or its underlying objects.
